Japanese straightening technique - a technique I learned YEARS ago and I whip out my skills when I know my client needs it ! This treatment is ideal for curly , thick , resistant hair . It will smooth out your hair so much it will be silky straight after every wash . The shine on this treatment is A+ also !

My client wanted to get rid of her uneven color and make it less warm . Unfortunately because it was so patchy this can be due to previous bleach or maybe different color formulas applied at every retouch . We needed to do a color correction , we needed to have a blank clean canvas and start all over . The process is lengthy and costly BUT you will get the best results and have a fresh start . After this a retouch is applied with color every 8 weeks and with the same exact formula to the T ! My client was so happy this color suits her so well 🤎🤎🤎🤎
